Goodness, I got caught.

20
00:04:28,851 --> 00:04:32,397
You wanted to come and roll around
on the sandy beach on your day off?

21
00:04:32,563 --> 00:04:34,399
I was going to stay quiet,

22
00:04:35,942 --> 00:04:37,527
but the guard post was way too old.

23
00:04:37,819 --> 00:04:39,779
Stop smiling. You're annoying me.

24
00:04:43,616 --> 00:04:44,993
What was it like to watch me in secret?

25
00:04:45,076 --> 00:04:47,370
I must have looked like a complete fool
to get so easily deceived

26
00:04:47,704 --> 00:04:48,913
to dance around.

27
00:04:48,997 --> 00:04:49,998
It was so pretty.

28
00:04:54,043 --> 00:04:55,378
It was really pretty.

29
00:04:56,379 --> 00:04:57,922
This part of my body felt itchy,

30
