A dress that is way too showy?

52
00:05:55,646 --> 00:05:56,856
My business smile?

53
00:05:57,106 --> 00:05:58,024
Don't be sarcastic.

54
00:05:58,107 --> 00:05:59,442
You know that this is necessary.

55
00:05:59,525 --> 00:06:01,569
Not all sponsors are perverted

56
00:06:01,694 --> 00:06:02,737
or dirty.

57
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:05,490
It's the dancer's job to receive attention
and endure it.

58
00:06:05,573 --> 00:06:07,283
Not yours, our outspoken director.

59
00:06:07,366 --> 00:06:09,827
Over the ten years
of my life as a director, I never made

60
