And it could be worse.

74
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,945
But still, we shouldn't
avoid this, Yeon-seo.

75
00:06:44,112 --> 00:06:45,029
I'll fight with you.

76
00:06:45,113 --> 00:06:47,156
I want to see you become the center

77
