of Fantasia.

78
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,915
I'll manage. Mind your business.

79
00:06:57,416 --> 00:06:58,417
Both of you.

80
00:07:23,317 --> 00:07:25,153
Is this what they call a dream?

81
00:07:31,284 --> 00:07:32,285
Goodness!

82
00:07:34,245 --> 00:07:36,164
How did you know about that beach?

83
00:07:36,247 --> 00:07:37,832
Even I couldn't remember,

84
00:07:38,124 --> 00:07:39,292
so how could you?

85
00:07:46,048 --> 00:07:48,968
You're smiling brightly, aren't you?

86
00:07:49,177 --> 00:07:50,219
You look pretty.

87
00:07:51,304 --> 00:07:53,014
Can you stop saying that?

88
00:07:53,097 --> 00:07:53,931
Are you teasing me?

89
00:07:54,015 --> 00:07:57,602
It is said that a useless servant
should do what he can.

90
